A Dust devil (elite) is an elite version of the dust devil. If on a Slayer assignment, an elite Dust devil is guaranteed to spawn; otherwise, elite monsters have a spawn rate of 1 in 1,000. Elite spawn rates can be further increased with the use of fellstalk incense sticks and tier 2 luck.

Unlike its normal counterparts, It will occasionally stun the player for 3 seconds at a time, so having Freedom and Anticipation will come in handy when facing it.
